2011-01-04 19:29  sg2

	* src/player.c: Fixed a crash occuring when --title-format is
	  specified at startup.

2011-01-04 19:18  sg2

	* plugins/output/disk_writer/writer.c: disk writer plugin:
	  introduce the name-as-title cfg option to let the output file be
	  named as the song title.

2011-01-04 19:12  sg2

	* plugins/input/cue/cue.c: cue plugin: set correct track number in
	  the song info.

2011-01-04 19:11  sg2

	* src/player.c: Introduce the cur-song-title cfg variable.

